parameters.name: DELTA_T
parameters.description: Length of data averaging window in millisecond.

parameters.name: BX
parameters.description:
Average of the X component of the magnetic field in                    
         PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description:
Average of the Y component of the magnetic field in                    
          PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description:
Average of the Z component of the magnetic field in                    
          PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BX^2
parameters.description:
Average of the square of the X component of the magnetic               
          field in PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BXBY
parameters.description: Average of the cross product of BX and BY in PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BXBZ
parameters.description: Average of the cross product of BX and BZ in PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BY^2
parameters.description: Average of the cross product of BX and BZ in PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BYBZ
parameters.description: Average of the cross product of BY and BZ in PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BZ^2
parameters.description:
Average of the square of the Z component of the magnetic               
          field in PE coordinates.

parameters.name: BX/|B|
parameters.description: Magnetic field vector directional cosine in X.

parameters.name: BY/|B|
parameters.description: Magnetic field vector directional cosine in Y.

parameters.name: BZ/|B|
parameters.description: Magnetic field vector directional cosine in Z.

parameters.name: |B|
parameters.description:
Average of the total magnetic field, evaluated as                      
          SQRT (BX^2 + BY^2 + BZ^2)

parameters.name: |B^2|
parameters.description:
Average of the square of the total field magnitude,                    
         evaluated as BX^2 + BY^2 + BZ^2
